## Technical

### Architecture
Client-side game with HTML5 Canvas for rendering, connected directly to Soundness Layer smart contracts for score storage and reward distribution. Frontend communicates directly with the blockchain through a wallet connector.

### Stack
Frontend: HTML5 Canvas + Vanilla JavaScript
Backend: Soundness Layer Smart Contracts (Rust)
Blockchain: Soundness Layer
Storage: WALRUS (permanent score storage) + LocalStorage (client-side temporary data)

### Features
Simple click/tap balloon gameplay mechanics
Decentralized leaderboard on the blockchain
NFT achievement system for special accomplishments
Token rewards for top players
Multi-mode gameplay (Classic, Time Attack, Endless)

